00:58:19,369 --> 00:58:20,369
<font color=#FFFF00>Gigit aku.</font>

802
00:58:20,369 --> 00:58:21,610
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan berbuat gegabah.</font>

803
00:58:21,610 --> 00:58:23,240
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku korban kekerasan seksual.</font>

804
00:58:23,240 --> 00:58:25,280
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan mengawasi.</font>

805
00:58:25,680 --> 00:58:27,340
<font color=#FFFF00>Sudah saatnya.</font>

806
00:58:27,749 --> 00:58:29,709
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ingin menemui ibumu.</font>

807
00:58:29,709 --> 00:58:30,880
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia sedang pergi?</font>

808
00:58:30,880 --> 00:58:32,419
<font color=#FFFF00>Bawa dia ke tempat tenang.</font>

809
00:58:32,419 --> 00:58:34,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak ada apa-apa di antara kalian, bukan?</font>

810
00:58:34,990 --> 00:58:37,119
<font color=#FFFF00>- Suamiku!/- Jaksa Ma.</font>

811
00:58:37,119 --> 00:58:38,189
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku siap.</font>

812
00:58:38,189 --> 00:58:41,030
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku siap menerima perasaanmu terhadapku.</font>

